          <h3>Approach</h3>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Manual code review</strong> - Human-in-the-loop analysis of security-critical paths</li>
            <li><strong>Automated scanning</strong> - Static analysis, dependency auditing, secret detection</li>
            <li><strong>Dynamic testing</strong> - Attempting documented attack patterns against running system</li>
            <li><strong>Architecture review</strong> - Evaluating trust boundaries and data flows</li>
          </ol>

          <h3>Disclosure</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>All critical and high findings fixed before public disclosure</li>
            <li>Findings summary published after remediation</li>
            <li>Full report available on request</li>
            <li>CVEs assigned where applicable</li>
          </ul>
